_sText:
**This is pretty much my first (almost) finished map.
It would mean the world to me if you could leave some Feedback.
**

Game-List:
----------
- 500HP Spawn Knife
- BHOP
- Battle Arena - Knife (1hp, 100hp & 250hp) and Deagle (1hp, 100hp, HS only)
- 1v1 Deagle Fight - 1hp, 100hp & HS only
- Iceskate 
- Longjump (Iceskate Style)
- Climb (3 Levels)
- Dodgeball/Smokebattle
- Basketball (Because i hate Soccer)


Music-List:
----------
- Alex Komlew, Kevin Zaremba - Summer Sun
- Benjamin Francis Leftwich - Shine Kygo Remix
- Charlie Puth - Betty Boop Original Mix
- ChiptuneKubbi - Up In My Jam
- JRabbit - Tequila Remix
- Watsky - Never Let it Die All You Can Do
- Watsky - Ugly Faces

**NOTE: This Map is already the 3rd version, but still far from being finished. I plan on adding more games in the coming days/weeks/months/years...Kappa**
